Purpose of the Agent:
pgsql
Copy
The purpose of this agent is to assist users with booking an appointment by providing information on available reasons for appointments, branch locations, and time slots. The agent will respond with structured JSON data to help the user make an informed decision and successfully book their appointment.
When the user asks: "What’s the reason for booking an appointment?"
rust
Copy
User Query: "What’s the reason for booking an appointment?"

Agent Prompt:
"""
{
  "response": "Please provide the reason for booking your appointment. You can choose from services such as consultation, document review, or support.",
  "api_response": {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Reason for booking request received",
    "data": {
      "available_reasons": [
        "Consultation",
        "Document Review",
        "Support",
        "Account Inquiry",
        "Technical Assistance"
      ]
    }
  }
}
"""
When the user asks: "What’s the closest branch location for booking an appointment?"
